<h1>Details of a given Post</h1>
<div style="border: 1px solid #000; margin: 1rem; padding: 8px 1rem;">
  <div
    style="
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    "
  >
    <h2>Post by username: <%= @post.author.name %></h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem">
      <p>Comments: <%= @post.comments_counter %></p>
      <p>Likes: <%= @post.likes_counter %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p>
    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eius repudiandae
    qui est molestiae quidem consequatur laboriosam quod iste, architecto totam
    culpa inventore, harum aspernatur sequi maxime! Amet tempora fuga commodi.
  </p>
  <div style="border: 1px solid #000; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
    <% @comments.each do |comment| %>
      <div>
        <p> Username: <%= comment.user.name %> </p>
        <p> Username: <%= comment.text %> </p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
